{"tid":826052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有網友屌我討論誇學科，通識性討論","createTime":"2018-09-18T03:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T06:11:28.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bed0e35ae7fbb7b25cd0c36c20fe67ee20dd72f","tid":826052,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"既然大家想要專業的學術討論，<br />\n我建議將來要咁定版規：<br />\n<br />\n如果你達唔到以下條件，唔可以在該領域或該學科發言：<br />\n<br />\n1 在相關領域工作5年以上，且月入35000或以上； 或<br />\n2 大學讀該科，2nd up或以上*；或<br />\n3 大學讀該科，2nd low或以上，兼做緊那科，且月入20000或以上；或<br />\n4 中學讀過，且成績在dse 5*或以上/高中校內90分或以上/或hkal grade C 或以上/hkcee grade A 。*<br />\n<br />\n*註：相關學歷如無相關工作經驗，假定10年後你腦海的相關知識會自動過期。即係無效。"},{"pid":"c03964618fdee6159e63a161264b630fab182099","tid":826052,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T03:30:58.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2251fb5796c77a5e12c74401be2e142fb715174","tid":826052,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"嗯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}